<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.2.3">
<l>kollā mākkōl kolaiceytu pāratappō</l>
<l>rellāc cēṉaiyu mirunilat tavittaventāy</l>
<l>pollā vākkaiyiṉ puṇarviṉai yaṟukkalaṟā</l>
<l>collāyyā ṉuṉṉaic cārvatōr cūḻcciyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O our father who, commiting murder with a stick of a horse that did not kill,</l>
<l>extinguished on the big ground the whole army of the Bhārata war,</l>
<l>without stopping to cut of the links to [my] wicked body</l>
<l>give [me] unique counsel about my joining you.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
